<p>Welcome to Episode 86 of <span style="color: #cc0000;">Light</span> <span style="color: #ffff00;">On</span> <span style="color: #660033;">Light</span> <span style="color: #339933;">Through</span>, in which I share a recently recovered voicemail from Marshall McLuhan, from August 1978, about my doctoral dissertation, "Human Replay: A Theory of the Evolution of Media," which I had mailed up to him in Canada, a few weeks earlier, before I left with my wife Tina on our summer vacation ...</p>
