        <item>
			<title>Time to Say Goodbye to Nuclear Energy</title>
            <link><![CDATA[http://paullev.libsyn.com/time-to-say-goodbye-to-nuclear-energy]]></link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p></p>
<div class="postBody">
<div class="postBody"><img src="http://asset-server.libsyn.com/item/1376435/assets/lolt1a.jpg" class="postImage" align="right" />The title of Episode 84 of <span style="color: #cc0000;">Light</span> <span style="color: #ffff00;">On</span> <span style="color: #660033;">Light</span> <span style="color: #339933;">Through</span> says it all:&nbsp; the continuing nuclear crisis in Japan shows why it's long since time to take our leave of nuclear power as a mainstream energy source on this planet.</div>
