</ol>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #6633cc;"><span style="color: #66ffff;"><span style="color: #990033;"><span style="color: #ff9999;"><span style="color: #000000;"><em>~playbill~</em></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #6633cc;"><span style="color: #66ffff;"><span style="color: #990033;"><span style="color: #ff9999;"><span style="color: #000000;"><em><strong>The Chronology Protection Case</strong></em></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #6633cc;"><span style="color: #66ffff;"><span style="color: #990033;"><span style="color: #ff9999;"><span style="color: #000000;">based on the story by Paul Levinson</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #6633cc;"><span style="color: #66ffff;"><span style="color: #990033;"><span style="color: #ff9999;"><span style="color: #000000;">radio adaption by Mark Shanahan, with Paul Levinson &amp; Jay Kensinger</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #6633cc;"><span style="color: #66ffff;"><span style="color: #990033;"><span style="color: #ff9999;"><span style="color: #000000;">directed by Elysa Martin</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #6633cc;"><span style="color: #66ffff;"><span style="color: #990033;"><span style="color: #ff9999;"><span style="color: #000000;">music performed by Bob Feldman</span></span></span></span></span></p>
