<li><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: small;">my <a href="http://www.myspace.com/paullevmusic">MySpace music page</a> ... <a href="http://www.facebook.com/pages/Paul-Levinsons-music/197340705490">Facebook fan page</a> ... <a href="http://www.reverbnation.com/paullevinson">Reverbnation</a></span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: small;"><a href="http://paullevinson.blogspot.com/2008/12/lyrics-to-paul-levinsons-twice-upon.html">complete lyrics</a> to the songs on <em>Twice Upon a Rhyme</em></span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: small;">links to <a href="http://paullevinson.blogspot.com/2007/11/little-taste-of-my-music.html">reviews and news</a> about Twice Upon a Rhyme</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: small;"><a href="http://paullevinson.blogspot.com/2011/01/twice-upon-rhyme-reviewed-in-shindig.html">Shindig Magazine</a> Jan-Feb 2011 review of Twice Upon a Rhyme<br /></span></span></li>
